No way!

09:40.980 --> 09:44.900
Seven drops is enough to lift a car.

09:44.900 --> 09:46.520
That is insane!

09:47.710 --> 09:49.830
Oh my God. We lifted a car with glue!

09:54.420 --> 09:55.180
This is amazing.

09:55.180 --> 09:57.400
We lifted a car with seven drops of glue.

09:57.400 --> 09:58.820
Now, I knew this stuff was strong,

09:58.820 --> 10:00.390
