31:09.010 --> 31:11.850
change of these traffic lights that will tells him

31:11.850 --> 31:14.520
which lane he has to swerve into at speed.

31:14.520 --> 31:15.990
They'll judge Adam's driving

31:15.990 --> 31:19.290
on how he preforms each maneuver as well as on his speed.

31:19.290 --> 31:22.690
Adam can't exceed 20 miles an hour going down the straightaway.

