31:24.450 --> 31:26.490
he can't exceed 25 miles an hour,

31:26.500 --> 31:29.660
and can't hit any cones or any pedestrians.

31:29.660 --> 31:31.540
Sober, with an empty bladder,

31:31.540 --> 31:33.880
Adam peels off three practice laps to

31:33.880 --> 31:35.630
get to grips with the course.

31:35.640 --> 31:37.790
And by starting with the full bladder test,

31:37.790 --> 31:41.710
Adam can enjoy his hangover once the testing is well and truely over.

31:41.710 --> 31:43.460
What's with the urgency room tent?

31:43.460 --> 31:44.870
Well this experiment about me getting

31:44.870 --> 31:46.920
a full bladder is not as simple

31:46.920 --> 31:48.620
as drinking a ton of water,

31:48.620 --> 31:50.320
having to pee, and then driving.

