35:24.460 --> 35:26.980
We've two identical super flat steel plates.

35:26.980 --> 35:29.130
This one is welded onto buster's frame,

35:29.130 --> 35:31.330
and the other welded into the car.

35:31.330 --> 35:35.420
And those two are stuck together with, yep, you guessed it.

35:35.420 --> 35:39.140
But will the super adhesive finally keep buster in the hot seat?

35:39.850 --> 35:41.580
All right, for our final experiment,

35:41.580 --> 35:43.750
we have the same circumstances as before.

