Here we go in 3, 2, 1.

35:47.240 --> 35:48.860
Looks good.

35:48.870 --> 35:51.610
We have one Buster just seat-belted in the passenger side

35:51.610 --> 35:55.090
and we have our main Buster, with two metal plates,

35:55.090 --> 35:58.880
super adhesive glued together, sitting in the driver's seat.

35:58.880 --> 36:01.460
Straight headed towards the K-rails.

36:03.690 --> 36:04.900
Hey, you know that might have worked!

