It might have worked!

36:07.700 --> 36:09.150
Well, what do you think?

36:09.910 --> 36:11.410
The plate's still connected.

36:11.410 --> 36:13.710
It actually withstood the crash.

36:13.720 --> 36:15.160
That's incredible.

36:15.160 --> 36:17.260
That's quite a super adhesive.

36:17.460 --> 36:18.410
This is incredible.

36:18.410 --> 36:19.800
He actually held on.

36:19.800 --> 36:22.380
The glue was strong enough to withstand this shock.

36:23.770 --> 36:24.840
I'm impressed.

36:24.950 --> 36:25.840
So am I.

36:25.840 --> 36:28.060
The super adhesive has stuck fast.

36:28.060 --> 36:32.990
And during an impact, impacting 16,000 pounds of force.

36:33.160 --> 36:36.450
Now in theory, super adhesive should have more than enough

36:36.450 --> 36:39.280
