with a 12 inch square steel plate welded to your back

36:49.070 --> 36:51.420
and a identical 12 inch square plate

36:51.420 --> 36:54.860
welded to a steel immovable chair in your car,

36:54.860 --> 36:56.610
it's not gonna work for you.

36:56.830 --> 36:58.730
Please, use a seat belt.

36:59.260 --> 37:02.010
Well, not going home in that car.

37:02.150 --> 37:03.120
Nope!

37:11.970 --> 37:13.640
At the other end of the runway,

37:13.660 --> 37:15.390
Adam couldn't be more ready

37:15.390 --> 37:17.840
to test his bladder impaired concentration.

37:17.850 --> 37:22.650
Bladder control test in 3, 2...

37:23.860 --> 37:25.220
Man, I'm gonna get even.

37:25.830 --> 37:27.820
One. Go.

